query:
SELECT
              g.seq AS "sequence!: EventSequence",
              e.id,
              e.payload AS "payload?",
              e.recorded_at AS "recorded_at?"
            FROM
                generate_series($1 + 1, $1 + $2) AS g(seq)
            LEFT JOIN
                cala_outbox_events e ON g.seq = e.sequence
            WHERE
                g.seq > $1
            ORDER BY
                g.seq ASC
            LIMIT $2
